name: Altergeist Kuntieri
desc: When an opponent's monster declares an attack while you control an "Altergeist" card: You can Special Summon this card from your hand, and if you do, negate the attack. If this card is Special Summoned: You can target 1 face-up card your opponent controls; while this monster is face-up on the field, that face-up card has its effects negated.
